OL,4,Cdiagnosis thanks community for help
OL,6,FA Jersey teacher who was left unable
OL,7,Fto work and struggling to make ends
OL,8,Fmeet when she was diagnosed with
OL,9,Fcancer last year says the money she
OL,10,Freceived from the island's Christmas
OL,11,FAppeal meant the world to her and her
OL,12,Ffamily.
OL,14,FEve Mann explains: "Because I couldn't
OL,15,Fwalk, they (Eve's husband and
OL,16,Fdaughter) had to help me with
OL,17,Feverything, every aspect of life.
