OL,4,Cdiagnosis thanks community for help
OL,6,F"We'd been struggling and thinking
OL,7,Fabout every penny. This just helped us
OL,8,Fto make sure that our Christmas dinner
OL,9,Fwas lovely, we had the electricity
OL,10,Fbill paid, and my daughter got a
OL,11,Fvoucher to spend.
OL,13,F"It made me realise that Jersey has
OL,14,Fgot a really caring community and if
OL,15,Fyou've never needed support before,
OL,16,Fyou don't really know what's out
OL,17,Fthere."
