OL,4,Cdiagnosis thanks community for help
OL,6,FSarah Richardson has benefited from
OL,7,Fthe charity fundraiser this year and
OL,8,Fsays: "I had a fall and I've broken my
OL,9,Fknee, so I can't get out that much.
OL,11,F"Putting the heating on does mean a
OL,12,Flot to me at the moment, especially
OL,13,Fthis year.
OL,15,F"I really would like to thank the
OL,16,FJersey Christmas Appeal and everyone
OL,17,Fwho supports and donates to them."
OL,19,FThis year's Christmas Appeal has
OL,20,Falready raised more than #55,000.
