OL,6,FIn 2024, a total of #75,000 went
OL,7,Ftowards helping around 1,500 islanders
OL,8,Fin need of financial support.
OL,10,FMoney is raised through donations and
OL,11,Fa charity auction, with successful
OL,12,Fbidders winning prizes including
OL,13,Fhelicopter rides, lunch with the Chief
OL,14,FMinister and a holiday at a ski chalet
OL,15,Fin France.
